title: fanoutqa: How many career rushing attempts do the first 5 running backs picked in the 2005 NFL draft each have? (3eb1b4b146c90359)

chat_history.content: How many career rushing attempts do the first 5 running backs picked in the 2005 NFL draft each have?

1. Ronnie Brown (2nd overall pick) — 1,145 attempts
2. Cedric Benson (4th overall pick) — 1,112 attempts
3. Cadillac Williams (5th overall pick) — 1,175 attempts
4. J.J. Arrington (44th overall pick) — 173 attempts
5. Eric Shelton (99th overall pick) — 54 attempts
